Detailed Description

This descriptor specifies the fields of the Transaction Error Interrupt Status register.

Field Documentation

Uint8 CSL_TAC_FE_transErrorInterruptStatus::errorFlag

Status of the error. A 1 indicates that an error occured.

Uint8 CSL_TAC_FE_transErrorInterruptStatus::masterId

The master ID on which the error occurred.

Uint8 CSL_TAC_FE_transErrorInterruptStatus::transId

The last available Transaction ID before the error occured.
